background_description: The image displays a well-furnished kitchen interior. Key features include cream-colored upper and lower cabinetry, a dark wood central island with a speckled granite countertop, and light wood flooring. The walls are painted a warm terracotta or burnt orange color, contrasted by white crown molding and trim. Stainless steel appliances, including a large refrigerator and built-in ovens, are prominent. There are also two wooden bar stools with green cushions at the island and a decorative golden horse figurine above the range hood.
